topic.title: Now Available: Twenty Newly Digitized Foreign Relations Volumes
topic.body: This release is part of the Office’s ongoing project, in partnership with the University of Wisconsin Digital Collections Center, to digitize the entire Foreign Relations series. These volumes cover events that took place between 1932 and 1939 and were originally published in print between 1947 and 1953.
